pull.title: test: Remove modinv python util helper function
pull.body: Since #27483 was merged the `modinv()` body is just one line calling pythons own implementation of `pow()`. We can just remove the function as it doesn't seem to add any value. Additionally the comment in the function is now outdated and the test is only testing two ways of doing modular inverse but both using python's `pow()` function.
